{
  "stem": "16503.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the major change was in March '39 when all of a sudden, up the street the Germans were marching in.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the first memory of the Germans coming in them was that what-- what's happening?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Look at all these soldiers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Don't forget I was nine-- not quite nine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, and I knew that the grownups were very, very upset and that whatever political-- they changed it into some kind of a-- there were some kind of a change in, in the political structure.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they called it-- I don't know what they called it anyhow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] that's about all it-- you know, it was a scary feeling seeing them because the scary feeling came from all these soldiers marching in.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I kind of sensed the scariness from the grownups.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I think that I did not comprehend what is going to happen or what it is all about in that sense.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "War wasn't spoken of.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The Sudetenland-- oh yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was one family which I did know about who went to the States, and that was a family who owned a textile shop where my father worked.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they closed down, and they went to the States.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They had great chalet just a few streets away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There was a part of that Prague where you had like housing, you know, with a garden and whatnot.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they were-- they were rich.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they, whatever they did, they got a visa for the whole family, and they went.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And my father had to-- that was-- I'm going back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "This is before the Germans came.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my father had to get a different job, which he did right away because he was well-known in his profession.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
